          <h2>Shares &amp; Dividends</h2>
          <p class="intro">
            How Hana shares are listed and traded, and how the company approaches
            dividends.
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="faqgroup">
          <details class="faq">
            <summary><span class="q">Where are Hana Microelectronics shares listed?</span><span class="chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="a">
              <p>Hana Microelectronics Public Company Limited is listed on the Stock Exchange of Thailand (SET) under the ticker symbol <strong>HANA</strong>. Shares are denominated and traded in Thai baht (THB).</p>
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary><span class="q">What is Hana's dividend policy?</span><span class="chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="a">
              <p>[Placeholder] Hana's policy is to pay dividends at a target payout ratio of the company's net profit, subject to the company's financial position, investment plans, and Board approval. Dividend payments are announced to the SET following Board and, where required, shareholder approval.</p>
              <p>Historical dividend records are available on the <a href="/investor-relations/news">Investor News</a> page.</p>
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary><span class="q">When does Hana pay dividends?</span><span class="chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="a">
              <p>[Placeholder] Dividends are typically considered alongside the full-year results and approved at the Annual General Meeting, with payment following the record date set in the SET announcement. Any interim dividend is announced separately.</p>
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary><span class="q">Does Hana offer a dividend reinvestment plan?</span><span class="chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="a">
              <p>[Placeholder] Hana does not currently operate a dividend reinvestment plan. Dividends are paid in cash to registered shareholders.</p>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ─── 3. Financial Reporting ─── -->
      <section class="doc" id="reporting">
        <header class="section-head">
          <div class="section-label">
            <span>4 questions</span>
