        <div class="faqgroup">
          <details class="faq">
            <summary><span class="q">What does Hana Microelectronics do?</span><span class="chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="a">
              <p>Hana Microelectronics is an electronics manufacturing services (EMS) and semiconductor assembly &amp; test (OSAT) provider. The group manufactures printed circuit board assemblies, integrated circuit packaging, RFID and smart-tag products, and sensor and optical modules for customers across automotive, industrial, medical, telecommunications, and other markets.</p>
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary><span class="q">Where does Hana operate?</span><span class="chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
