              <p>Hana is headquartered in Thailand and operates manufacturing facilities across Thailand, China, Cambodia, and the United States. Details of each site are on the <a href="/locations">Locations</a> pages.</p>
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary><span class="q">When was Hana listed on the SET?</span><span class="chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
